# Copy to .env.local and add at least one API key.
# Without any keys, the app runs in fallback mode (hash-based instruments/kits, no LLM).
#
# Providers are tried in order: Anthropic → OpenAI → Gemini → DeepSeek → xAI
# When one hits a rate limit or fails, the next is tried automatically.
# Text tasks (kit generation): all 5 providers supported.
# Vision tasks (instrument identification): Anthropic, OpenAI, Gemini, xAI only (DeepSeek no vision).

# Anthropic Claude (recommended for vision accuracy)
# Get key at: https://console.anthropic.com/account/keys
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# OpenAI GPT-4o
# Get key at: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...

# Google Gemini
# Get key at: https://ai.google.dev/
# GEMINI_API_KEY=...

# DeepSeek (text only, no vision)
# Get key at: https://platform.deepseek.com/api_keys
# DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=sk-...

# xAI Grok
# Get key at: https://console.x.ai/
# XAI_API_KEY=...
